Gibson’s Gourmet Burgers & Ribs offers a whopping 207 milkshakes. CAPE TOWN - A milkshake selection at a Cape Town restaurant is in the Guinness Book of World Records. Gibson’s Gourmet Burgers & Ribs offers a whopping 207 milkshakes. The slick restaurant group’s Ian Halfon said they were elated. “We started following the trend. Some of the biggest trends were vegan, sugar-free, yoghurt, goats milk and all kinds of different combinations. It just built up.” Halfon said despite the grand selection, chocolate is still the firm favourite. 